#. <section class="sutta" id="sn52.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn52.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 52"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 52"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn52.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Rahogatavagga"
msgstr "1. In Private"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn52.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Tatiyakaṇḍakīsutta"
msgstr "6. At Thorny Wood (3rd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn52.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāketanidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāketa."

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ anuruddhaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Sāriputta said to Anuruddha:"

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.3"
msgid ""
"“katamesaṃ āyasmā anuruddho dhammānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ "
"patto”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“What things has Venerable Anuruddha developed and cultivated to attain "
"great direct knowledge?”"

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ khvāhaṃ, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"mahābhiññataṃ patto."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, I attained great direct knowledge by developing and cultivating "
"the four kinds of mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.5"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.6"
msgid ""
"Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, kāye kāyānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya "
"loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"I meditate observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of "
"desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.7"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "I meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.8"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.9"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.10"
msgid ""
"imesaṃ khvāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"mahābhiññataṃ patto."
msgstr ""
"I attained great direct knowledge by developing and cultivating these four "
"kinds of mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn52.6:1.11"
msgid ""
"Imesañca panāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"sahassaṃ lokaṃ abhijānāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation that I directly know the entire galaxy.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn52.6:1.12"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
